org.cytoscape.io.read

Interface VizmapReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Task

    public interface VizmapReader
extends Task
    An extension of the Task interface that returns a VisualStyle object. Instances of this interface are created by InputStreamTaskFactory objects registered as OSGi services, which are in turn processed by associated reader manager objects that distinguish InputStreamTaskFactories based on the DataCategory associated with the CyFileFilter.

    Cytoscape Backwards Compatibility (SPI Interface): We expect that this interface will be implemented. Therefore to maintain backwards compatibility this interface will only be modified for major version updates.

    Module: io-api

    To use this in your app, include the following dependency in your POM:

    <dependency>
    <groupId>org.cytoscape</groupId>
    <artifactId>io-api</artifactId>
</dependency>
